data.name: CreateTributeText
data.value:
Now that your tribute has been created, its time to add content!
You could start by creating the story where visitors to the tribute can find out moe about who the tribute is dedicated to. Or, you could post a new event related to the new tribut, and invite people too. Photo albums and videos are also great place to start - it is really up to you!
What we can tell you is that the best tribute sites are the ones that have content on them - so that visitors will spend time exploring and will be encouraged to contribute.
